suncertify
Class Application

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.Application

public class Application
extends Object

Class Application is a controller of application. It is a startup application class also.
It has references to the most important objects:

  • DBAccess for database operating
  • ApplicationOptions for options operating
  • RecordSocketServer for networking interaction

Version:
1.0
Author:
Petr Shilkin
